---
title: Beef Koftas & Cucumber Couscous with Garlic Yoghurt
description: Spice up your mealtime with beef koftas! Juicy, savoury and packed with flavour, these bundles of joy go perfectly with a vibrant couscous salad and tangy garlic yoghurt. Load up your plate and dig in.

